	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>St Thomas</placeName> <date>14 Sept 1857</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd Mr Leeser</addressee></p>
				<p><placeName>Phila</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">My Dr Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">I received your<lb/> favor of the <date>2d Dec</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I was glad to find that<lb/> the congregation of your late<lb/> ministry had at length done<lb/> the act of justice that they so<lb/> long defined&#44; by sending you<lb/> a copy of the annal of the<lb/> con<add>&#63;</add> so improperly <sic>passid</sic> on<lb/> you&#8212;on your part it is your<lb/> <hi rend="underline">duty</hi> to attend the Synagogue<lb/> frequently&#44; &#38; thereby <add>&#63;</add> to</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>them that no truce of ill will<lb/> exists.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I have collected 2 years<lb/> subscription from three subscribers<lb/> myself being one&#44; &#38; have sold<lb/> the last set of the Pentateuch<lb/> &#38; daily &#38; festival prayers&#44; no<lb/> more remain&#8212;my Son has sold<lb/> the set of the Pentateuch received<lb/> with the Bibles&#44; the money for<lb/> which will be paid later.  I<lb/> would recommend you to send<lb/> him three sets of the Daily &#38;<lb/> Festival prayers&#44; finely bound<lb/> provided you can Invoice them<lb/> at about &#36;20 three sets of the</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p><add>&#63;</add> like last &#38; three sets<lb/> of the Pentateuch they are now<lb/> &#38; then conquered after</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed the Bank of St<lb/> Thomas&#39; Bell No 8235 at sight<lb/> on <persName>J C Whitmore</persName> for &#36;42&#8212;as<lb/> payment in fall for</p>
				<p>1 set of the Pentateuch &#36;12</p>
				<p>1 &#8220; of D &#38; F Prayer&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;12</p>
				<p>2 year subscription of</p>
				<p>3 subscribers to Occident <hi rend="underline">18</hi></p>
				<p>&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#36;42&#8212;</p>
				<p>I regret I cannot prevail on<lb/> our people to subscribe&#44; those that<lb/> are appertain to my family</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Mrs W</persName> joins in kind regards<lb/> &#38; we beg you to also give them<lb/> our friends the <persName>Florences</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">Yours truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">A. Wolff</persName></p>
				<p>I have collected &#163;35 towards<lb/> the testimonial to the late<lb/> Lord Mayor of <placeName>London</placeName> <persName>D.<lb/> Solomons</persName></p>
			<pb n="Envelope&#44; Recto"/>
				<p><addressee>Revd Mr I Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philada.</placeName></p>
			<pb n="Envelope&#44; Verso"/>
				<p><add>&#63;</add><lb/> forward by <persName>Mr<lb/> <add>&#63;</add></persName> &#38;c</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><hi rend="underline"><persName>D Wolff</persName></hi></p>
		</body>
